{"id":7939,"date":"2024-01-20T01:29:45","date_gmt":"2020-04-19T19:59:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=7939"},"modified":"2024-06-10T18:21:01","modified_gmt":"2024-06-10T12:51:01","slug":"new-style-kitchen-trends","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/new-style-kitchen-trends\/","title":{"rendered":"The Heart Wants What It Wants! Newest Kitchen Trends in 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Newest trends for your modular kitchen. The heart of your home! A place where memories are homemade, seasoned with love.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Every year, homeowners look forward to the latest trends to revive the style quotient of their homes. Kitchens always top this plan. In the year 2023, kitchens were all about space-saving, storage, and kitchen islands. So what is dominating the modular kitchen designs in 2024 thus far?&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We checked in with the designers at Design Cafe to find out the newest kitchen trends that have dominated the market and the wishlists of our homeowners this year. Whether you are planning a complete kitchen renovation or few changes here and there our kitchen trends for 2024 will keep excited. Now that you know how the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-design-trends-2022\/\">kitchen design trends 2024<\/a>&nbsp;are different from the kitchen design trends 2023.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Marble Kitchen Countertops<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Marble is no news! Classic and elegant marble countertops come in a wide variety all the way from Rajasthan to Italy. It has a lovely natural pattern that makes it unique. Another great thing about marble kitchen countertops is that they blend in with every kitchen style. Besides, marble is a classic that stands the test of time. It makes it the top kitchen trend for 2024.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19185236\/marble-countertop-with-new-style-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"New kitchen design trends with marble countertops which are classic and elegant\" class=\"wp-image-7942\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19185236\/marble-countertop-with-new-style-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19185236\/marble-countertop-with-new-style-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19185236\/marble-countertop-with-new-style-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19185236\/marble-countertop-with-new-style-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/10-different-types-of-kitchen-countertops\/\">10 Different Types Of Kitchen Countertops<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make Way For Kitchen Larders!&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For those of you wondering what a kitchen larder is, it\u2019s a smart unit to help the quintessential chef in you. A larder is a prep-station where your ingredients are cut, peeled, chopped, sliced and measured before they hit the grill! A larder further houses mixing bowls, appliances, and equipment to keep your countertop free.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19192822\/newest-kitchen-trends-with-kitchen-larders.jpg\" alt=\"High end new kitchen trends with kitchen larder where your ingredients are cut\" class=\"wp-image-7947\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19192822\/newest-kitchen-trends-with-kitchen-larders.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19192822\/newest-kitchen-trends-with-kitchen-larders-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19192822\/newest-kitchen-trends-with-kitchen-larders-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19192822\/newest-kitchen-trends-with-kitchen-larders-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Functional modular kitchen interiors for a classic culinary experience\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/10175752\/functional-modular-kitchen-interiors-for-classic-culinary-experience.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Let Your Wall-Papers Do The Talking!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The trendiest addition to 2024\u2019s kitchen designs! Wallpapers add character and flair to otherwise dull and boring kitchen walls. They are extremely durable as they are resistant to heat, water and grease, making it perfect to spruce up your kitchen. They come in a plethora of patterns and colours to suit every taste and style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19193528\/modern-kitchen-design-trends-2020-with-kitchen-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"New kitchen design trends with wallpaper which are resistant to heat, water and grease\" class=\"wp-image-7948\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19193528\/modern-kitchen-design-trends-2020-with-kitchen-wallpaper.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19193528\/modern-kitchen-design-trends-2020-with-kitchen-wallpaper-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19193528\/modern-kitchen-design-trends-2020-with-kitchen-wallpaper-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19193528\/modern-kitchen-design-trends-2020-with-kitchen-wallpaper-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-wallpaper-designs\/\">Modern Kitchen Wallpaper Designs For Your Home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Space To Hide Kitchen Appliances<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Appliances tucked behind the panels in a&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">modular kitchen<\/a>&nbsp;out of sight lend a clean, minimal and uncluttered aesthetic. This design is a popular pick this year as modern families have little to no time to clean and tidy up their kitchens. Hiding kitchen appliances is a smart way to keep the dirt away from the seldom-used ones.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19194206\/place-to-hide-kitchen-appliances-with-latest-kitchen-design-trends.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen trends 2022 with a space to hide kitchen appliances is a smart way to keep the dirt away\" class=\"wp-image-7949\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19194206\/place-to-hide-kitchen-appliances-with-latest-kitchen-design-trends.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19194206\/place-to-hide-kitchen-appliances-with-latest-kitchen-design-trends-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19194206\/place-to-hide-kitchen-appliances-with-latest-kitchen-design-trends-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19194206\/place-to-hide-kitchen-appliances-with-latest-kitchen-design-trends-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lots Of Texture And Some More!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For those who shy away from bold colours, focus on adding textures. Used unlacquered brass strap hooks and knobs on drawers and cabinets, marble countertops, laminates on shutters and tons of&nbsp; wooden flooring will bring in the right feel to your kitchen.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19203111\/new-style-kitchen-with-lots-of-texture.jpg\" alt=\"Current kitchen trends with lots of texture\" class=\"wp-image-7950\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19203111\/new-style-kitchen-with-lots-of-texture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19203111\/new-style-kitchen-with-lots-of-texture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19203111\/new-style-kitchen-with-lots-of-texture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19203111\/new-style-kitchen-with-lots-of-texture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Colourful Touch<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A pop of colour never goes out of style. Dip your toe in a pool of colours, this year bring in colourful cabinets, bright walls and vibrant pottery.&nbsp; Or you can also paint a large portion of your kitchen to add a hint of colour to this space. This is one of the current kitchen trends too for 2024!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19204930\/newest-kitchen-trends-2020-with-colourful-touch.jpg\" alt=\"High end kitchen design trends with a colourful touch with cabinet , bright walls and vibrant pottery\" class=\"wp-image-7951\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19204930\/newest-kitchen-trends-2020-with-colourful-touch.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19204930\/newest-kitchen-trends-2020-with-colourful-touch-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19204930\/newest-kitchen-trends-2020-with-colourful-touch-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/19204930\/newest-kitchen-trends-2020-with-colourful-touch-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/8-best-colour-combinations-for-kitchen\/\">8 Best Colour Combinations For Your Kitchen<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Two Is Better Than One!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you feel a monochromatic palette can be overpowering or get outdated\/boring after a while, pick a colour combination for your modular kitchen. Dual-toned kitchens have become a popular choice in the last few years and are expected to be one of top trends for 2024. So get over the idea of having the complete white kitchen and pick a combination that screams your style and gives it a million-dollar look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155625\/Two-is-better-than-one.jpg\" alt=\"Best kitchen trends 2022 with two colour combination\" class=\"wp-image-7992\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155625\/Two-is-better-than-one.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155625\/Two-is-better-than-one-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155625\/Two-is-better-than-one-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155625\/Two-is-better-than-one-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Deck Up Your Kitchen With Copper Accents<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Copper accents have become the symbol of luxury lately. They have slowly made their way into almost every corner of the modern houses \u2013 lights, furniture, decor items \u2013 copper is literally everywhere! This year, it\u2019s making its way into the modular kitchens. So follow the trend and introduce copper accents to your kitchen. If you are not a big fan of it, try gifting your cabinets a copper knob or add a few copper lights to see the magic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20004107\/high-end-kitchen-design-trends-with-copper-accents.jpg\" alt=\"Latest kitchen design trends with copper accents with lights, furniture and decor items \" class=\"wp-image-7953\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20004107\/high-end-kitchen-design-trends-with-copper-accents.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20004107\/high-end-kitchen-design-trends-with-copper-accents-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20004107\/high-end-kitchen-design-trends-with-copper-accents-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20004107\/high-end-kitchen-design-trends-with-copper-accents-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read&nbsp;About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/modular-kitchen-materials-and-finishes\/\">A Guide To Materials And Finishes For Kitchen<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Concealed Range Hoods<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are guilty of paying more attention to your appliances, kitchen accessories or the backsplash, then you\u2019re surely on your way to embrace this hottest, newest kitchen trend for 2024. Put the other kitchen elements under the spotlight with a sleek and modern concealed range hood that blends in beautifully with your former cabinets.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155043\/concealed-range-hood-for-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen trends 2022 with concealed range hoods\" class=\"wp-image-7988\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155043\/concealed-range-hood-for-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155043\/concealed-range-hood-for-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155043\/concealed-range-hood-for-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/20155043\/concealed-range-hood-for-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And that\u2019s all for now. Let us know which idea did you like the most in the comments below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.